GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 7th April, 1958.
The undersigned is directed to say that Hafiz
Mohammad Ibrahim has taken over charge of the Ministry of
Irrigation and Power from Shri S.K. Patil with effect from
the forenoon of the 2nd April, 1958.
2. The undersigned is also directed to say that Shri B.
Gopala Reddi assumed office as Minister of Economic Affairs
with effect from the 2nd April, 1958.
3. The following Deputy Ministers also assumed office
on the same date:-
1. Shri S.V. Ramaswamy
2. Shri Ahmed Mohiuddin
